Isaac Dean v. Caroline P. Ford.Appeal from the Superior Court of Cook County.Charles Pickler, attorney for appellant.E. F. Gorton and George W. Brown, attorneys for appellee.

Decree of foreclosure, affirmed because of incomplete transcript of record, on Troy L. M. Co. v. Kelling, 167 Ill. 495, and Culver v. Schroth, 153 Ill. 437, and for other reasons shown in opinion filed.
